Yes! Transit Gateway also connects AWS to On-premises.

Normal VPN vs Transit Gateway VPN:

# Without Transit Gateway ❌
On-Premises ←→ VPC1 (separate VPN)
On-Premises ←→ VPC2 (separate VPN)
On-Premises ←→ VPC3 (separate VPN)
# 3 separate VPN connections!

# With Transit Gateway ✅
On-Premises ←→ Transit Gateway ←→ VPC1
                                ←→ VPC2
                                ←→ VPC3
# Single connection — hub and spoke model!

                    ┌─────────────────┐
                    │  Transit Gateway│
                    └────────┬────────┘
          ┌─────────────┬────┴────┬─────────────┐
          ↓             ↓         ↓              ↓
        VPC1          VPC2      VPC3         On-Premises
                                            (via VPN/DX)
